title: Now That's Music - Flashback's  2016 320ak
description:
Now That's Music - Flashback's 2016 320ak

Well since I launched this recurring monthly release of my picks I have noticed that It seems to be working for ya. Thank you for that. 
I put out a monster size version of this last year and it was too much to soon. Thats OK with me cause it set up the opportunity for me to do these.

This series of releases will be music that made me the uploader I am now. But as always the keys to the future lie in the picks from the past

So Now I Bring Flashbacks...
